title: Sudden Strike Pack
description:
This torrent contains the following games :

1) Suddenstrike 3 (needs daemontools to install )   [ENGLISH]

2) Suddenstrike 2 (and Real Warfare Mod 6.71 )      [ENGLISH]

3) Suddenstrike Forever                             [ENGLISH]

4) Suddenstrike Univers                             [GERMAN]

5) Suddenstrike Resource War                        [ENGLISH]

6) Hidden Stroke 2                                  [ENGLISH]


And also have included some tools :

1) GameSpy Arcade(you can find players to play multiplayer SS3 ,SS2 and Forever )

2) Daemontools(you need it to install some of this game especially Suddenstrike 3)
